title: Chaos Alchemist
summary: Gu Yun, a young gifted genius, is reduced to doing odd jobs at the Qing Shan sect because his spiritual energy was weakened from an ancient god’s seal. His father was also implicated, and had his role as head of the Qing Shan sect stripped, and was imprisoned by the opposing Feilu family. At this time, Gu Yun discovers the secret hidden within his body, and forms a pact with the ancient god…
